            <Icon name="lucide:compass" class="w-7 h-7" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Terpental dari Tab For You</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Mesin kurasi melewatkan konten Anda begitu saja akibat absennya dorongan interaksi awal, membuat cuitan mustahil menjangkau target market di luar lingkar pengikut.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 bg-blue-900 text-white overflow-hidden relative">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/image/manfaat-jasalike-instagram.png')] opacity-10 bg-cover bg-center mix-blend-overlay"></div>
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 text-center">
